237
00:22:40,759 --> 00:22:42,279
but it doesn't really matter.

238
00:22:46,599 --> 00:22:47,839
Why is your voice hoarse?

239
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:53,000
Did you stay up late again
last night?

240
00:22:58,200 --> 00:22:59,359
Anyway, from now on,

241
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,000
take good care of yourself.

242
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,880
All right then.

243
00:23:10,119 --> 00:23:11,200
Next week,

244
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:14,680
I'll go back to Jiangzhou
for a business trip.

245
00:23:15,279 --> 00:23:16,680
I'll go home...

246
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,720
and get my belongings.

247
00:23:30,319 --> 00:23:31,880
We're both adults.

248
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:34,960
Let's part on good terms.

249
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,680
When you come back,

250
00:23:47,799 --> 00:23:48,839
I'll make you...

251
00:23:49,839 --> 00:23:50,880
your favourite...

252
00:23:51,599 --> 00:23:52,640
sweet and sour pork ribs.

253
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:08,960
By the way,
let me ask you something.

254
00:24:09,079 --> 00:24:10,359
Is my caller's name on your phone...

255
00:24:10,839 --> 00:24:12,119
