256
00:24:13,799 --> 00:24:14,838
It's Su Su.

257
00:24:14,839 --> 00:24:15,839
What's the matter?

258
00:24:16,079 --> 00:24:17,920
Will you change it
since we broke up?

259
00:24:31,519 --> 00:24:32,559
No.

260
00:25:27,519 --> 00:25:29,119
Han Han, can you do me a favour?

261
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,960
Why are you being so polite
all of a sudden?

262
00:25:32,079 --> 00:25:33,160
What is it? Tell me.

263
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:34,480
Here's the thing.

264
00:25:34,759 --> 00:25:37,279
I've been managing
my friend's house...

265
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:38,480
while he's overseas.

266
00:25:38,599 --> 00:25:40,359
He plans to rent it out...

267
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,880
and a new set of furniture
is being delivered today.

268
00:25:43,519 --> 00:25:44,758
However,
I'm currently out in the suburbs...

269
00:25:44,759 --> 00:25:45,839
and can't make it back.

270
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,880
Can you help me receive
the furniture?

271
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:50,640
That place is very close
to your company.

272
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,599
It's about a 10-minute walk.

273
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:54,640
I'll send you the keys
via courier later.

274
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:56,480
I thought it was something serious.

275
00:25:56,559 --> 00:25:57,598
No problem.

276
00:25:57,599 --> 00:25:58,920
I'll go there at noon.

277
00:25:59,279 --> 00:26:01,200
Ask the furniture delivery guy
to contact me directly.

278
00:27:03,559 --> 00:27:04,599
Why do you live so far away?

279
00:27:05,079 --> 00:27:07,039
You must spend a lot of time
commuting every day.

280
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,758
I can't afford to rent
a place closer to the company.

281
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:10,960
I'll rent it for you.

282
00:27:12,599 --> 00:27:14,999
I've been managing
my friend's house.

